Brangvyne
Greetings )
I would like to do this. I have just created a wiz on

me know. Otherwise sure anywhere you wanna go is fine
with me.

--- Brangvyne <brangvyne7@...> wrote:
> Salutations All!
>
> I've been playing some nwn recently with a few
> friends on Friday
> evenings and was wondering if there might be some
> interest in forming
> an EQ group to meet on one evening a week and
> adventure together for
> a while. We could start a set of new characters and
> bring them up as
> a group. I would be willing to meet on whatever
> server and be
> whatever class or race that was needed. We could
> form a little party
> and help each other out. I thought it might be fun.
> Is there anyone
> else who has any intrest in an idea like this.
>
> If so let's discuss the details.
>
> :o)
> Brangvyne
>
